Axon (formerly TASER International) is a Scottsdale, Arizona-based company which develops products for the law enforcement market.
Its flagship product and former namesake is Taser, a line of electroshock weapons. The company has since diversified into technology products for law enforcement, including body cameras and digital evidence solutions; as of 2017, body cameras and associated services comprise a quarter of Axon's overall business.[1]



